StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetApplicantPackageTypeAssigned_User]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @PackageTypeAssigned_UserID uniqueiden..er ) AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT DISTINCT p.Title, p.LastName, p.FirstName, p.MiddleName FROM Person AS p INNER JOIN Personnel AS pl ON p.PersonID = pl.PersonID INNER JOIN ApplicantPackage AS ap ON ap.PackageTypeAssigned_UserID = pl.UserID WHERE ap.PackageTypeAssigned_UserID = @PackageTypeAssigned_UserID
